@ClunkTheSkunk I am

Continuing on design: As for the colors, I chose blue, specifically sky blue, for the fur color because I love the color and the daytime sky. The accent color is black not just because I love the color black, but also because it blends nicely with the fur color.
Design: Since this is my first attempt at drawing an OC (mine or not), I tried to do a cartoon-style drawing of a fox and also it's based on my unsuccessful attempts at drawing my anthro OC.

Name: The first name is my actual first name. The last name is different. I was looking for a South Asian Muslim name that starts with a K, is short and easy to remember, and is not Khan, since that one is too common. I settled with Kazi.

Species: Fox because I couldn't decide between a dog and a cat, and learning that foxes are like dogs on the outside and cats on the inside, I decided to choose that. Also, foxes are cute and are relatively simple to draw. https://t.co/vnx6ZrHmJ8
